    <item>
      <title>莫迪利用 1974 年与斯里兰卡的岛屿协议来攻击反对派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/modi-uses-1974-island-deal-with-sri-lanka-to-attack-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪指责主要反对党在五年前执政时将一座岛屿割让给斯里兰卡，挖掘了一个敏感问题，着眼于在南部邦赢得选票，而印度人民党未能在该邦赢得选票。牵引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/modi-uses-1974-island-deal-with-sri-lanka-to-attack-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 08:19:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大使称美印关系并未因谋杀阴谋调查而受损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/us-india-ties-not-damaged-by-murder-plot-probe-ambassador-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻印度大使表示，他对印度在调查去年涉嫌密谋杀害一名锡克教活动人士方面取得的进展感到高兴，并补充说这个问题不会妨碍两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/us-india-ties-not-damaged-by-murder-plot-probe-ambassador-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 05:24:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对派席卷土耳其地方选举后里拉下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/lira-dips-after-turkey-opposition-parties-sweep-local-elections-lugi5xc7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安领导的执政党在周日的地方选举中惨败，包括伊斯坦布尔和安卡拉在内的土耳其许多城市的控制权落入反对派手中，土耳其里拉走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/lira-dips-after-turkey-opposition-parties-sweep-local-elections-lugi5xc7</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 05:21:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪的反对派团结起来要求公平选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/modi-s-opposition-unites-in-delhi-rally-seeking-fair-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，数万人与数十名反对派领导人一起聚集在印度首都，呼吁举行自由公正的选举——并抗议逮捕包括德里首席部长在内的几位高级政治领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/modi-s-opposition-unites-in-delhi-rally-seeking-fair-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 04:42:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尹敦促韩国医生返回，并为会谈留出空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/s-korea-s-yoon-urges-doctors-to-return-leaves-room-for-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈表示，他不会放弃增加医学院席位的计划，同时为长达数周的争议留出谈判空间，这场争议已导致韩国几乎所有实习医生罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/s-korea-s-yoon-urges-doctors-to-return-leaves-room-for-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:17:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普拉博沃在海上紧张局势中前往日本之前将与习近平会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/xi-set-to-meet-indonesia-s-prabowo-in-china-amid-tensions-at-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托将于周一在北京会见中国领导人习近平，然后在南海紧张局势升级之际前往日本进行类似的高层会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/xi-set-to-meet-indonesia-s-prabowo-in-china-amid-tensions-at-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 02:52:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本议员表示美国钢铁交易将有助于应对中国风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/japan-s-amari-says-us-steel-deal-would-help-counter-china-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本执政党一位资深议员表示，新日铁公司收购美国钢铁公司将加强美国和日本之间的经济安全联系，并有助于对抗中国在钢铁生产领域的主导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/japan-s-amari-says-us-steel-deal-would-help-counter-china-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 02:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱并不认为阿根廷在中期投票前美元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/milei-doesn-t-see-argentina-dollarizing-before-midterm-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱并不认为他的政府在明年中期选举之前将经济美元化，这为他在竞选中最雄心勃勃的经济提案的时间表提供了初步线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/milei-doesn-t-see-argentina-dollarizing-before-midterm-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 02:31:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安在土耳其市政选举中遭遇历史性失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/turkey-municipal-elections-erdogan-set-for-shock-defeat-against-main-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 在投票箱中对主要反对党遭遇了前所未有的失败，原因是通货膨胀猖獗，借贷成本达到二十多年前总统上台以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/turkey-municipal-elections-erdogan-set-for-shock-defeat-against-main-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 20:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
